    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo discusses Flow Attribute Notification Protocol (FANP), which is a protocol between neighbor nodes for the management of cut-through packet forwarding functionalities.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
